title: Suzanne Brockmann - Troubleshooters 1-16
description: I Downloaded this series about six months and just got around to converting it to .m4b.  When I looked to see, if any more audiobooks in this series had been uploaded, I could not find the old torrent anymore, so I am reuploading this series.  The series is at 80 kbps,and sounds good.  I have put the series in 4 .m4b files.  I had to brake up the series because if, you make a .m4b file larger than 3.99 GB the file will not play to the end.  I like to listen to series with as little number of files as possible, so I do not have to switch from file to file so much.  I think .m4b is the best format to listen to audiobooks because it saves where you are at in the book.
